{"tid":1458882,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[民間記者會]同學們,如果有時間,可以學習下快必既演說技巧","createTime":"2019-08-12T15:20:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T01:39:02.000Z","uid":188176,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2ec6809dbe092ee315d983a7510936a5e31d244e","tid":1458882,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:20:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pe0oQm2icbY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dpe0oQm2icbY&d=1ZU4T503J%2FBBtE%2F0CauWlcls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=fabed133\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pe0oQm2icbY</a><br />\n先唔好講立場同個人喜好<br />\n快必既演說的確係香港黎講算幾出色<br />\n眼神,動作,道具,語速,各方面都合格以上,洽到好處<br />\n令人好容易掌握到重點去寫稿<br />\n個人覺得民間記者會內容係夠<br />\n但我自己同身邊既人都覺得係缺乏左演說既魅力<br />\n人地聽個時易悶同失去左方向<br />\n記者亦都好難重點寫稿<br />\nANYWAY,你地已經做得好好,要愈做愈好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ff0ffc5495f6bafc54eac77289fe97872874ba1","tid":1458882,"uid":2419,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:21:13.000Z","msg":"好可惜呢個係慢必黎"},{"pid":"64a6e1654b76d0ace702bc3b78caf0cf9cf4e8f0","tid":1458882,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:21:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ab35450fe7e6e14bcd0cc413792de4e262a60a","tid":1458882,"uid":63779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:24:52.000Z","msg":"純粹以代議士黎講基佬陳算OK，帶表情等黎有道理，論述清晰易明，有少許立場但不失理性，可惜得把口。"},{"pid":"a39989af44c480938ec4fe13d5123f507aa3f4fd","tid":1458882,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ff0ffc5495f6bafc54eac77289fe97872874ba1","tid":1458882,"uid":2419,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:21:13.000Z","msg":"好可惜呢個係慢必黎"},"citedBy"